<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Thank You — Geometrik Studio</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>
:root {
  --ink: #151515;
  --muted: #5f6470;
  --navy: #232c55;
  --blue: #3769e8;
  --green: #55d3ad;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #ffffff;
  color: var(--ink);
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.wrap {
  width: min(820px, 90%);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 80px 20px;
}

.logo {
  width: 88px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.kicker {
  color: var(--blue);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 92px);
  line-height: .95;
  letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  margin: 0 0 28px;
}

p {
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin: 0 auto 36px;
  max-width: 620px;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 15px 26px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: var(--green);
  color: var(--navy);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 800;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="wrap">
  <img src="images/Geometrik logo.png" alt="Geometrik Studio" class="logo">

  <div class="kicker">Message sent</div>

  <h1>Thank you.</h1>

  <p>
    Your project request has been received.  
    We’ll review the details and get back to you shortly.
  </p>

  <a href="https://geometrik.co.uk" class="btn">Back to homepage</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
